      • fillCollection

        public static <E> void fillCollection(java.util.Collection<E> collection,
                                      Fetcher<E> fetcher,
                                      boolean autoClose)
        Filling the specified collection by elements from specified fetcher.
        Type Parameters:
        E - type of elements retrieved from fetcher.
        Parameters:
        collection - specified collection which is filled in by elements from specified fetcher.
        fetcher - specified fetcher which is iterated to retrieve its elements which are filled in the specified collection.
        autoClose - if true, the fetcher is automatically closed after the filling task is finished.
